# F21DV Road Safety Data Story
Group 10 · F21DV · Dubai Campus · 2026

> An interactive data story built for law enforcement agencies, exploring Victoria road crash patterns from 2012–2025.

## Project Structure

```
f21dv_gp_dubai_10/
├── data/
│   ├── accident.csv              ← raw 
│   ├── vehicle.csv               ← raw 
│   ├── person.csv                ← raw 
│   ├── processed_accidents.csv   ← generated by preprocess.py
│   ├── processed_persons.csv     ← generated by preprocess.py
│   └── processed_vehicles.csv   ← generated by preprocess.py
├── libs/
│   └── d3/
│       └── d3.min.js             ← D3.js v7
├── scripts/
│   ├── main.js                   ← All D3 charts, filters, interactions
│   └── preprocess.py             ← One-time Python data cleaning script
├── styles/
│   └── main.css                  ← All CSS — dark theme, layout, chart styles
├── index.html                    ← Single-page application entry point
└── README.md                     ← This file
```


## Getting Started

### 1. Preprocess the data (one time only)

```bash
pip install pandas
python scripts/preprocess.py
```

### 2. Run a local server

```bash
python -m http.server 8000
```

Then open **http://localhost:8000** in your browser.

